title: Pics! Jacqueline Fernandez Goes Shopping In London
text:
Posted by: Vinod D'souza Published: Thursday, October 15, 2015, 18:27 [IST] 
After wrapping up the shoot of Housefull 3 in London, Jacqueline Fernandez hits the streets and went shopping with her sister. The actress shared a lot of fun filled pictures on her Instagram account roaming the streets of London.Jacqueline Fernandez is currently shooting in London for Housefull 3 along with Lisa Haydon and Nargis Fakhri . The lead actors in the movie are Akshay Kumar , Abhishek Bachchan and Riteish Deshmukh.Sajid Nadiadwala, has casted Akshay Kumar in all the three Housefull franchises and the movie is a comedy roller coaster.Recently we saw pictures of Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna roaming the city of Norwich taking a day off from the shoot of Housefull 3 , and now Jacqueline Fernandez is seen chilling with her sister in London.Click on to see some awesome pictures of Jacqueline Fernandez shopping in London with her sister.
